nodes.text: This clone naval officer was stationed on the bridge of a Venator-class Star Destroyer and served under the command of Jedi Master Adi Gallia around 21 BBY during the events of the Battle of Patitite Pattuna. After the Separatists began their attack on Adi Gallia's flagship, this Clone naval officer was ordered by Gallia to start the evacuation after the ship's main reactor was damaged.
